      "author": "ysf-ad",
      "description": "Release 1.0.12\n\n- Adds wildcard target exclusion patterns for noisy/index-style notes, with defaults for _Index and _index_ naming conventions.\n- Adds ignored match terms so configured words or phrases are never auto-linked.\n- Adds manual retargeting from each suggestion context dropdown, letting users override a matched phrase to a different file before applying.\n- Applies target pattern exclusions to deterministic and semantic matching.\n- Adds regression coverage for wildcard target exclusions and ignored match terms.",
      "downloadCount": 5,
